{"tid":1817200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"韓國光州電視台短片，對比 1980 光州與今天的香港","createTime":"2020-01-09T01:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T05:20:22.000Z","uid":287557,"like":79,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"17f754d082b8c380d06d0fbf2cd6c07c42dcec62","tid":1817200,"uid":287557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T01:21:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jxQV29LZSls&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjxQV29LZSls%26feature%3Demb_title&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF08wxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=27a904d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jxQV29LZSls&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\n每每同韓國朋友提起當下香港抗爭的畫面，他們都會不期然地聯想起光州 1980 年的「5.18」起義 。<br />\n<br />\n最近韓國光州 KBS 電視台，便製作了一條短片，把過去半年多香港那些在抗爭現場發生的示威與警察鎮壓片段，跟 1980 年光州「5.18」起義，曾經出現過的類似畫面，作一對照。<br />\n<br />\n從示威者對民主的熱情、結集的陣勢、叫喊的歌曲、民眾無私付出之情，到軍警動用武力鎮壓示威者的畫面，意外地兩件事雖然相隔近 40 載，但當中的情境，竟然如斯地相似。<br />\n<br />\n當年，光州沒有放棄；今天，香港人也要繼續加油！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%89%E5%B7%9E%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%8F%B0%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87-%E5%B0%8D%E6%AF%94-1980-%E5%85%89%E5%B7%9E%E8%88%87%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF/?fbclid=IwAR3S0JgqH8Kqpm_YxhNEIjh4O0bpdb3BlvflOgCSCz2XXZKvRMiSj-H97Wo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25B7%259E%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25AF%2594-1980-%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25B7%259E%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3S0JgqH8Kqpm_YxhNEIjh4O0bpdb3BlvflOgCSCz2XXZKvRMiSj-H97Wo&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF08wxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=fe48d397\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25B7%259E%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25AF%2594-1980-%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25B7%259E%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3S0JgqH8Kqpm_YxhNEIjh4O0bpdb3BlvflOgCSCz2XXZKvRMiSj-H97Wo&h=0bf5ef88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%89%E5%B7%9E%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%8F%B0%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87-%E5%B0%8D%E6%AF%94-1980-%E5%85%89%E5%B7%9E%E8%88%87%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF/?fbclid=IwAR3S0JgqH8Kqpm_YxhNEIjh4O0bpdb3BlvflOgCSCz2XXZKvRMiSj-H97Wo</a>"},{"pid":"569d57ed313ab12fe4470b2e9a3d146b3661cbc8","tid":1817200,"uid":45727,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T01:34:02.000Z","msg":"光州事件1980 年5月發生, 持續咗1個月就被壓下去, 然後到1987 年先被認同, 再發生6月民主運動, 泡菜國才有總統直選<br />\n到40年後今日, 光州事件平反調查都仲未完, 香港人仲有好長嘅路要走"},{"pid":"acd27ba56c48c24436134a935928d2725aa17447","tid":1817200,"uid":39842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T01:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b17d24e1aa2a52756b52b78104944a22616cda","tid":1817200,"uid":64880,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"569d57ed313ab12fe4470b2e9a3d146b3661cbc8","tid":1817200,"uid":45727,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T01:34:02.000Z","msg":"光州事件1980 年5月發生, 持續咗1個月就被壓下去, 然後到1987 年先被認同, 再發生6月民主運動, 泡菜國才有總統直選<br />\n到40年後今日, 光州事件平反調查都仲未完, 香港人仲有好長嘅路要走"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T01:49:58.000Z","msg":"就算你同我講話20年之後先可以完全清算黑警同埋涉事高官 我都會等"},{"pid":"3d58f2201b5d7a5f3f8e13ae64980320e58076d4","tid":1817200,"uid":287557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:53:25.000Z","msg":"P can't push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />